                     <interp inst="t18390204-615-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18390204-cd-80" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390204-615-offence-1 t18390204-cd-80"></join>27th of De<lb></lb>cember</rs>, 5 caps, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18390204-name-477" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18390204-name-477" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
